  "image": "/img/ai-homepage/real-impact-01.webp",
  "prompt": "Create a single standalone HTML file (no build tools, no npm, no frameworks). The entire page must work by opening the .html file directly in a browser.\n\nOUTPUT REQUIREMENT:\n- One complete .html file only\n- All CSS inside <style> tags in <head>\n- All JavaScript inside <script> tags at the bottom of <body>\n- No external CSS files, no Tailwind CDN, no JavaScript frameworks\n- Only allowed external resources: Google Fonts via <link>, Unsplash images via <img src>\n\n---\n\nDESIGN: HTML Attributes — Reference Document Layout\n\nFONTS (load via Google Fonts):\n  Plus Jakarta Sans: weights 300, 400, 500, 600\n  Fira Code: weights 400, 500\n  Preload primary font woff2 with fetchpriority='low' crossorigin\n\nCSS VARIABLES (:root):\n  --bg: #f5f4f0          (warm off-white page background)\n  --surface: #ffffff     (card/panel surface)\n  --border: #e4e2dc      (light divider)\n  --border-dark: #c8c5bc (stronger divider)\n  --ink-1: #18171a       (primary text)\n  --ink-2: #48464f       (secondary text)\n  --ink-3: #8a8794       (muted/label text)\n  --code-bg: #1c1b20     (dark code block background)\n  --code-text: #c9c6d0\n  --code-tag: #e8877a    (HTML tag color)\n  --code-attr: #82bfdb   (attribute name color)\n  --code-val: #7dc89a    (attribute value color)\n  --code-cmt: #585560    (comment color, italic)\n  --font-sans: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif\n  --font-mono: 'Fira Code', 'Courier New', monospace\n  --r-sm: 4px  --r-md: 8px  --r-lg: 12px\n  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.04)\n  --shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08), 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04)\n\nBASE STYLES:\n  * box-sizing border-box, margin 0, padding 0\n  html: font-size 16px; scroll-behavior smooth\n  body: font-family var(--font-sans); background var(--bg); color var(--ink-1); line-height 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing antialiased\n\n---\n\nSTICKY NAVIGATION (.nav):\n  position sticky; top 0; z-index 100\n  background: rgba(245,244,240,0.92); backdrop-filter blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter blur(12px)\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)\n  Inner (.nav-inner): max-width 900px; margin auto; padding 0 24px; height 52px\n    display flex; align-items center; justify-content space-between; gap 16px\n  Brand (.nav-brand): font-size .75rem; font-weight 600; letter-spacing .08em; text-transform uppercase; color var(--ink-1)\n    Text: 'HTML Attributes'\n  Nav links (.nav-links): display flex; gap 4px; list-style none\n    Each <a>: padding 4px 10px; border-radius var(--r-sm); font-size .78rem; font-family var(--font-mono); color var(--ink-3)\n    hover: background var(--border); color var(--ink-1)\n    .active: background var(--ink-1); color #fff\n    Links: #loading, #fetchpriority, #autocomplete, #inputmode\n    Hide on mobile (max-width 640px)\n\n---\n\nHERO SECTION (.hero, inside .page):\n  .page: max-width 900px; margin auto; padding 0 24px 80px\n  .hero: padding 64px 0 48px; border-bottom 1px solid var(--border)\n  Eyebrow (.hero-eyebrow): inline-flex; gap 8px; font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .72rem; font-weight 500\n    letter-spacing .1em; text-transform uppercase; color var(--ink-3); margin-bottom 20px\n    ::before pseudo: width 24px; height 1px; background var(--border-dark)\n    Text: 'Reference Boilerplate'\n  H1: font-size clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem); font-weight 300; line-height 1.18; letter-spacing -.02em; color var(--ink-1); margin-bottom 16px\n    Text: 'Four attributes.<br><strong>Real impact.</strong>' (strong has font-weight 600)\n  Subtitle (.hero-sub): font-size 1.05rem; color var(--ink-2); max-width 520px; font-weight 300; line-height 1.65; margin-bottom 36px\n    Text: 'No JavaScript. No visual change. These attributes give the browser the context it needs to load faster, prioritise smarter, and serve the right keyboard.'\n  Pill row (.pill-row): display flex; flex-wrap wrap; gap 8px\n    Each pill (.pill): inline-flex; gap 6px; padding 5px 12px; background var(--surface); border 1px solid var(--border)\n      border-radius 999px; font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .75rem; color var(--ink-2); box-shadow var(--shadow-sm)\n      Dot (.pill-dot): 6px circle; background var(--ink-1)\n    Pills: loading, fetchpriority, autocomplete, inputmode\n  Hero image (.hero-img-wrap): margin-top 40px; border-radius var(--r-lg); overflow hidden; box-shadow var(--shadow-md)\n    Image: src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?w=1200&q=80'\n      width 100%; height 340px; object-fit cover; filter grayscale(10%) brightness(.97)\n      loading='eager' fetchpriority='high' width='1200' height='600'\n    Badge (.hero-img-badge): position absolute; bottom 14px; left 14px; padding 5px 10px\n      background rgba(24,23,26,.78); backdrop-filter blur(6px); border-radius var(--r-sm)\n      font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .65rem; color rgba(255,255,255,.75)\n      Text: \"loading='eager' · fetchpriority='high' · width + height set\"\n\n---\n\nSECTION STRUCTURE (repeat for each of 4 sections):\n  .section: padding 56px 0 0; add class 'reveal' for scroll animation\n  Section header (.section-header): display flex; align-items flex-start; gap 20px; margin-bottom 28px\n    Number box (.section-num): 36x36px; border 1px solid var(--border-dark); border-radius var(--r-sm)\n      font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .72rem; color var(--ink-3)\n    Section tag (.section-tag): padding 2px 8px; background var(--code-bg); color var(--code-attr)\n      border-radius var(--r-sm); font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .75rem; margin-bottom 6px\n    h2: font-size 1.5rem; font-weight 500; letter-spacing -.02em; color var(--ink-1); line-height 1.25\n  Section body text (.section-body): font-size .95rem; color var(--ink-2); line-height 1.7; margin-bottom 20px; max-width 640px\n  Inline code (code.inline): font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .84em; background rgba(24,23,26,.07)\n    padding 1px 5px; border-radius 3px; color var(--ink-1)\n  Section divider (.section-divider): height 1px; background var(--border); margin-top 56px\n\nCARD COMPONENT (.card):\n  background var(--surface); border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius var(--r-lg)\n  overflow hidden; box-shadow var(--shadow-sm); margin-bottom 16px; class 'reveal'\n  Card head (.card-head): padding 14px 20px; border-bottom 1px solid var(--border)\n    display flex; align-items center; justify-content space-between; gap 12px\n    Title (.card-head-title): font-size .75rem; font-weight 600; letter-spacing .06em; text-transform uppercase; color var(--ink-3)\n    Badge (.card-head-badge): font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .68rem; color var(--ink-3); padding 2px 7px\n      border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius 999px\n  Card body (.card-body): padding 20px\n\nCODE BLOCK (.code-wrap):\n  background var(--code-bg); border-radius var(--r-md); margin-bottom 16px; overflow hidden; class 'reveal'\n  Code bar (.code-bar): display flex; justify-content space-between; padding 10px 16px\n    border-bottom 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)\n    Dots (.code-dots): 3x 8px circles; background rgba(255,255,255,.12); gap 5px\n    Label: font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .68rem; color rgba(255,255,255,.3)\n  <pre>: padding 16px 20px 20px; font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .8rem; line-height 1.8\n    color var(--code-text); overflow-x auto; white-space pre\n  Syntax classes: .ct (tag, red), .ca (attr, blue), .cv (value, green), .cc (comment, gray italic)\n\nCALLOUT (.callout):\n  display flex; gap 12px; padding 14px 16px; background var(--bg)\n  border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius var(--r-md); margin-bottom 16px; class 'reveal'\n  Icon (.callout-icon): flex-shrink 0; width 18px; font-size .85rem (use ⚠ or ℹ)\n  Text: font-size .875rem; color var(--ink-2); line-height 1.6\n\n---\n\nSECTION 01 — loading (id='loading'):\n  Num: 01 | Tag: loading | H2: 'Defer what the user can't see yet'\n  Body: explain loading='lazy' defers below-fold images; always include explicit width/height to prevent CLS\n  Card 1 (title: 'Image loading comparison', badge: 'DevTools → Network to verify'):\n    2-column image compare grid:\n      Left: img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d14bab8c?w=800&q=70'\n        height 180px; object-fit cover; border-radius var(--r-md); filter grayscale(18%)\n        loading='eager' fetchpriority='high'\n        Caption badge: [eager] 'Loads immediately'\n      Right: img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=800&q=70'\n        loading='lazy'\n        Caption badge: [lazy] 'Deferred until near-viewport'\n    Badges: .badge-dark (background var(--ink-1), color #fff), .badge-light (background var(--border))\n  Card 2 (title: 'Lazy-loaded iframe', badge: 'loading=\"lazy\"'):\n    OpenStreetMap iframe: src='https://www.openstreetmap.org/export/embed.html?bbox=-0.12,51.49,-0.09,51.51&layer=mapnik'\n      loading='lazy'; height 240px; filter grayscale(35%)\n    Caption explaining loading='lazy' works on iframes too\n  Code block (label: 'HTML'): show eager hero image + lazy below-fold image + lazy iframe examples with syntax coloring\n  Callout (⚠): 'Never use loading=\"lazy\" on images visible when the page first opens.'\n\nSECTION 02 — fetchpriority (id='fetchpriority'):\n  Num: 02 | Tag: fetchpriority | H2: 'Tell the browser what matters first'\n  Body: explain fetchpriority='high' moves hero image to front of loading queue\n  Card (title: 'Loading queue — bandwidth allocation'):\n    Priority bars (.priority-bars): 5 rows with animated fill bars\n      Row structure (.pbar-row): label (140px wide) + track + badge\n      .pbar-track: height 8px; background var(--bg); border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius 999px\n      .pbar-fill: height 100%; background var(--ink-1); border-radius 999px; width starts at 0\n        transition: width 1.2s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1); data-w attribute = target percentage\n      Rows: hero.jpg(88%) fetchpriority=high | main.css(72%) render-blocking | section-img.jpg(38%) default | analytics.js(12%) fetchpriority=low | secondary-font(8%) fetchpriority=low\n  Code block (label: 'HTML — <head>'): preload hero high + preload font low + LCP img eager+high + analytics defer+low\n  Callout (ℹ): loading=eager prevents deferral; fetchpriority=high wins bandwidth; both belong on hero image\n\nSECTION 03 — autocomplete (id='autocomplete'):\n  Num: 03 | Tag: autocomplete | H2: 'Tell the browser what each field holds'\n  Body: explain 50+ token values beyond on/off; new-password triggers password generation\n  Form Cards (4 cards):\n    Card 1 'Personal details & login': given-name, family-name, email+inputmode=email, tel+inputmode=tel, username, current-password, new-password\n    Card 2 'Shipping address': street-address, postal-code+inputmode=numeric, address-level2, country\n    Card 3 'Payment' (badge: cc-name · cc-number · cc-exp · cc-csc): cc-name, cc-number+inputmode=numeric, cc-exp+inputmode=numeric, cc-csc+inputmode=numeric\n    Card 4 'One-time verification code' (badge: one-time-code):\n      Explain autocomplete=one-time-code + inputmode=numeric triggers iOS SMS autofill\n      Input: maxlength=6, pattern=\\d{6}\n  FORM STYLES:\n    .form-grid: display grid; grid-template-columns 1fr 1fr; gap 12px (cols-1=1fr, cols-3=1fr 1fr 1fr)\n    .field: display flex; flex-direction column; gap 5px\n    label: font-size .7rem; font-weight 500; letter-spacing .05em; text-transform uppercase; color var(--ink-3)\n    input: width 100%; padding 9px 12px; font-family var(--font-sans); font-size .9rem; color var(--ink-1)\n      background var(--bg); border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius var(--r-sm); outline none\n      focus: border-color var(--ink-1); background var(--surface)\n    .form-rule: height 1px; background var(--border); margin 16px 0\n  Code block: current-password, new-password, one-time-code+numeric, cc-number+numeric+pattern\n\nSECTION 04 — inputmode (id='inputmode'):\n  Num: 04 | Tag: inputmode | H2: 'Show the right keyboard on mobile'\n  Body: explain inputmode controls virtual keyboard only, not validation; more flexible than type\n  Card 'All inputmode values — tap each on mobile':\n    3-column grid (.im-grid): 6 items\n      Each item: badge label + labeled input field\n      .im-badge: padding 1px 6px; background var(--border); color var(--ink-2); border-radius 3px; font-family var(--font-mono); font-size .65rem\n      Values: numeric (0-9 only), decimal (0.00), tel (telephone), email (@ shortcut), url (/ and .com), search (Enter→Search)\n  Code block: numeric, decimal, OTP (autocomplete+inputmode together)\n  Callout (ℹ): desktop shows regular field; mobile shows different keyboards per inputmode\n\n---\n\nFOOTER:\n  margin-top 64px; padding-top 28px; border-top 1px solid var(--border)\n  display flex; justify-content space-between; align-items center; gap 16px; flex-wrap wrap\n  Text: 'No JavaScript · No visual change · Four attributes · Real impact.' (font-mono, .78rem, ink-3)\n  Tags (.footer-tags): 4 pill tags — loading, fetchpriority, autocomplete, inputmode\n    Each: padding 3px 8px; border 1px solid var(--border); border-radius 999px; font-mono; .65rem; ink-3\n\n---\n\nJAVASCRIPT — place in <script> at bottom of body:\n\n1. SCROLL REVEAL (IntersectionObserver):\n  Base: .reveal elements start opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px); transition opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease\n  .reveal.visible: opacity 1; transform none\n  Observer threshold 0.08: when intersecting → add 'visible' class + animate priority bars + unobserve\n  Priority bar animation: when section-02 card becomes visible,\n    querySelectorAll('.pbar-fill[data-w]').forEach(bar => bar.style.width = bar.dataset.w + '%')\n\n2. NAV ACTIVE STATE (IntersectionObserver):\n  Watch all section[id] elements with rootMargin '-40% 0px -55% 0px'\n  When section intersects: remove 'active' from all nav links, add 'active' to matching href link\n\n---\n\nRESPONSIVE (max-width 640px):\n  .form-grid, .form-grid.cols-3, .img-compare, .im-grid → grid-template-columns 1fr\n  .nav-links: display none\n  .pbar-label: width 90px; font-size .65rem"
}